00:02:29.693 --> 00:02:32.485
- Força.
- Sim.


12
00:02:47.110 --> 00:02:48.360
Vamos lá, pais.

13
00:02:48.443 --> 00:02:52.193
Peguem nos pequenotes
e entrem no saco com eles.


14
00:02:52.527 --> 00:02:56.985
